  "title": "3206 E 25th Ave, Vancouver - 5 beds/3 baths",
  "description": "VIEW! VIEW! VIEW! Welcome to this well-maintained custom-built 5 Bed, 3 Bath family home offering over 2,200 sq.ft of living space on a desirable CORNER LOT. The spacious main floor features bright living and family areas, with dining opening to a west-facing patio showcasing beautiful city and mountain views. Upstairs offers 3 beds, 2 baths, and a balcony to enjoy the mountain scenery. Includes a 2-bedroom unauthorized suite with separate entrance&mdash;an excellent mortgage helper. Plenty of parking w/ a 2-car garage + additional lane and front street parking. Just a short walk to Renfrew Ravine Park, Renfrew Community Centre, 29th Ave Station, Windermere Secondary and Renfrew Community Elementary. A fantastic opportunity in a convenient, family-friendly location! OH on Feb 28(SAT), 2-4pm ",
